                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2000-05-15</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This was another fantastic book by the same people who brought you Strategic Selling. It provides the blocking and tackling of sales situations that fills out the strategic approach of their earlier book. <P>This is a professional, mature approach to selling that is sadly rare in the profession.</span>
                  
              
